column15: Hescott Shoot Hartland Bideford, Devon https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/hescott-shoot-hartland pheasant, Driven. 30-40 in a bag/day, predominantly pheasant

Clovelly Shoot approx 230, 124 pheasant and partridge https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/clovelly-shoot both syndicate and driven days. Driven days = up to 400 birds, syndicate days of up to 300 birds
Hayne Barton https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/hayne-barton pheasant + other, driven. 2 miles from Holsworthy. Beat one stand one. Mostly pheasants. 2 teams of 5-6 alternating drives
Sydenham Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/sydenham-shoot Pheasant and Partridge, Driven, Mini-driven. 200-400 birds/day. 15 drives across 2000 acres. 4-5 drives per day
Bovacott Park https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/bovacott-park Pheasant, Driven, 120 birds/day near Holsworthy/Great Torrington

Hembury Castle (near Torrington) Pheasant https://www.shootinguk.co.uk/shooting/shoot-reports/game-shooting-at-hembury-castle-devon-11611 Google Earth – 242, 116 https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/hembury-castle-estate-shoot pheasant, driven. Bag = 150-200 birds. Approx 6 drives per day
Duntz valley (could be Duntz hill or Duntz river (242, 120) pheasant, between 150/250 birds/day, covers 1000 acres  https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/duntz-valley-shoot
Warleigh Barton Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/warleigh-barton-shoot Driven. Spanning 480 acres. 5 drives/day. Near Plymouth, borders Dartmoor. Pheasant and Partridge
Gulworthy Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/gulworthy-shoot pheasant and partridge, Driven. 100-250 bird days. Situated on devon/cornwall border. 5 drives per day
Langtree Lake Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/langtree-lake-shoot Pheasant, Driven. valley following the Langtree Lake for 2.5km. 1000 acres in size. Bags between 80 and 150 birds
The Totleigh Barton Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/the-totleigh-barton-shoot Pheasant, Driven. 500 acres. Bag of 50-60 birds. 5 drives approx per day

Heanton Satchville in the Torridge Valley (halfway between Great Torrington and Hatherley https://www.thefield.co.uk/shooting/the-20-best-pheasant-shoots-in-britain-30528 Google Earth – Between 240, 110 and 250, 100 (approx 253, 111), 5,000 acres with 25 drives, 250-300 birds a day
Whitsleigh Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/whitsleigh-shoot Pheasant, Driven. 90-100 bird/day. Near Great Torrington
Hollamoor, Tawstock https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/hollamoor-tawstock Pheasant Driven. 2 miles south of Barnstaple. Max 7 drives per day

Brownstone Estate Shoot near Yealmpton (South Devon)https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/brownstone-estate-shoot Pheasant and Partridge, Driven. 140-200 pheasant per shoot. Average of 165/day. 10 drives

The Cornwood Shoot PL21 9QX https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/the-cornwood-shoot Driven, Pheasant and Partridge. Set in the Dartmoor national park (two estates: Delamore and Watercomble/Blachford) covers 6500 acres of land, providing 20 different drives approx 250 birds per day. 4 drives/day
Fox and Hounds Country Hotel, Chulmleigh, Devon – EX18 7JZ (Pheasant) https://www.foxandhoundshotel.co.uk/devon-activities-attractions/shooting-in-devon/ Google Earth – 260, 110
Temple shoot, Castle Hill Estate in Bray valley https://fieldsports-journal.com/article/temple-shoot Googe Earth (266, 128) 2,500 acre
North Molton Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/north-molton-shoot 15,000 acres on the southwest fringe of Exmoor. Pheasant and Partridge. Driven.

Morleigh Valley Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/moreleigh-valley-shoot pheasant and partridge. Driven. 30 acres. Bag totals between 70-100 birds. 4000 pheasants shot through the season. 5 drives a day

Great Fulford Shoot http://www.greatfulfordshoot.co.uk/ Google Earth  https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/great-fulford-estate-shoot 3000 acres on the edge of Dartmoor – 12 miles from exeter, daily bag = 150-350 birds, pheasant and partridge approx 6 drives per day

Molland, Bettws Hall, Devon (Pheasant And Partridge) https://www.shootinguk.co.uk/shooting/game-shooting/pheasant-shooting/pheasant-partridge-shooting-molland-devon-40670 Google Earth – 280, 120, 5000 acres, 30 drives

Cornworthy court farm https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/cornworthy-court-farm pheasant, Drivenand minidriven. 300 acres. Releases 500 birds per season. Shoot days bagging around 30 birds. 9 drives to choose from (syndicate?)

Frost Farm Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/frost-farm-shoot pheasant, Partridge, Driven. 400+acres. Put down 3000 birds, predominatly pheasant but also partridge and duck, near bovey tracey and Moretophamstead

Higher Crockham Far, Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/higher-crockham-farm-shoot predominantly pheasant, Driven. The farm buys and rears one-month-old pheasants on a small scale from mid-june onwards. North of Bovey Tracey
Culver – just says birds. At least 2 drives/day https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/culver

Ugbrooke Park, Devon (near Chudleigh) Pheasant https://www.shootinguk.co.uk/shooting/game-shooting/pheasant-shooting/pheasant-shooting-at-ugbrooke-park-devon-11265 https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/ugbrooke-park-shoot Google Earth – 286, 76. 15 mins from central exeter, pheasant partridge and duck (250-400 birds per day) 6 drives per day
Ashcombe Estate https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/ashcombe-estate 2,500 acres in South Devon , nearly 30 drives – ten miles west of exeter. approx 4 drives per day,  Pheasant and partridge
Aishe Barton Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/aishe-barton-shoot Driven, phesant and partridge 2 drives (as well as 1 duck drive) 50-200 birds/day. Set within 3500 acres
Loyton Lodge, Exe Valley (Tiverton) https://www.thefield.co.uk/shooting/the-20-best-pheasant-shoots-in-britain-30528 Google earth, 6000 acres along the Exe valley
Huntsham Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/huntsham-shoot Pheasant, Partridge. Huntsham estate = 5000 acre situated on Exmoor foothills . Average bags between 250-400. Approx 5 drives/day
Combe Estate https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/combe-estate Pheasant and Partridge, Driven and mini-driven. 4000 acre Estate. Approx 100-150 birds/day. Near Honiton and Ottery st Mary
Blannicombe (East Devon) 15 mins from Exeter Airport, pheasant and partridge, Bag size = 200, driven shoot, 5 drives per day https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/blannicombe Driven
Beer Shoot on Devon Clinton Estate https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/beer-shoot driven, pheasant. Shooting over 1500 acres located between Beer and Branscombe
Bovey Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/bovey-shoot walk one stand one. 6 drive/day. 65-90 birds. Pheasant and Partridge. 2000 acres. Near Sidmouth and Seaton
The Cotleigh Shoot (near Honiton) Pheasant https://www.shootinguk.co.uk/shooting/shoot-reports/the-cotleigh-shoot-4708 Google Earth – Approx 320, 102, 600 acres
East Devon shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/east-devon-shoot pheasant and partridge, Driven. Usually 5 or six drives. Covers Seaton, Lyme Regis and Axminster

Blackdown (hills) Shoot https://www.gunsonpegs.com/shoots/devon/blackdown-shoot Driven and walked-up 450 acres pheasant, partridge, duck 80-100 mixed bird days. 5/6 drives/day. Near Chard and Ilminster
